      <title>国泰航空走出政府阴影 因新冠疫情贷款即将偿还</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/cathay-out-from-government-shadow-as-covid-loan-set-to-be-repaid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港国泰航空有限公司周五宣布，将回购香港政府为帮助其在疫情期间维持运营而借出的总值 195 亿港元（25 亿美元）优先股的剩余一半，标志着该公司在新冠疫情复苏过程中又迈出了重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/cathay-out-from-government-shadow-as-covid-loan-set-to-be-repaid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
