    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布前美国国债上涨是美联储前景的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/treasuries-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员期待美国月度就业报告，市场普遍预计该报告将显示劳动力市场逐渐降温，从而可能增强货币政策放松的理由，美国国债收益率全线小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/treasuries-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
