    <item>
      <title>投资者称工党获胜后英国资产重获青睐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-assets-are-back-in-favor-after-labour-victory-investors-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默领导的工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利后，英国资产重新受到青睐，这让人们希望英国能迎来一段政治平静时期，并稳定国家财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-assets-are-back-in-favor-after-labour-victory-investors-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:40:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据或为宽松政策提供线索，黄金有望周度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gold-pushes-higher-as-investors-expect-fed-will-start-to-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储将在年底前降息，黄金价格连续两周上涨，交易员们正在关注美国非农就业数据，以寻找下一批经济前景的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gold-pushes-higher-as-investors-expect-fed-will-start-to-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布前全球股市创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在关键的美国就业数据公布之前，全球股市创下历史新高，预计就业数据将显示出招聘有所放缓。随着工党在英国大选中获胜，英镑创下了四年来最长的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
